{"title":"DNS协议","date":"2020-03-13T14:48:57.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 13, 2020","L":"03/13/2020","MM-DD":"03-13"},"thumbnail":"post/计算机网络/DNS协议/cover.jpg","link":"post/计算机网络/DNS协议","categories":["计算机网络"],"updated":"2020-03-13T14:53:15.299Z","content":"<h1 id=\"dns层次\">DNS层次<a href=\"#dns层次\" title=\"DNS层次\"></a></h1><img src=\"/post/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/DNS%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/image-20200313212044898.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<h2 id=\"根域\">根域<a href=\"#根域\" title=\"根域\"></a></h2><p>根节点，为空。</p>\n<h2 id=\"顶级域\">顶级域<a href=\"#顶级域\" title=\"顶级域\"></a></h2><p><a href=\"http://www.baidu.com其中com为顶级域\" target=\"_blank\">www.baidu.com其中com为顶级域</a></p>\n<ul><li>com</li>\n<li>org</li>\n<li>net</li>\n<li>...</li>\n</ul><h2 id=\"二级域\">二级域<a href=\"#二级域\" title=\"二级域\"></a></h2><p>一般为公司名或者组织名。<a href=\"http://www.baidu.com其中baidu为二级域\" target=\"_blank\">www.baidu.com其中baidu为二级域</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"dns解析过程\">DNS解析过程<a href=\"#dns解析过程\" title=\"DNS解析过程\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"递归解析\">递归解析<a href=\"#递归解析\" title=\"递归解析\"></a></h2><p>DNS解析请求层层传递，最后层层返回。</p>\n<ul><li>用户只需请求一次</li>\n<li>服务器压力大</li>\n</ul><img src=\"/post/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/DNS%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/image-20200313212331163.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<h2 id=\"反复解析\">反复解析<a href=\"#反复解析\" title=\"反复解析\"></a></h2><p>用户请求服务器时，服务器若不能给出结果，则会告诉用户接下来要找谁去解析，让用户自己请求</p>\n<ul><li>用户请求多次</li>\n<li>服务器压力小</li>\n</ul><img src=\"/post/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/DNS%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/image-20200313212429620.png\" class=\"\">","prev":{"title":"HTTP协议","link":"post/计算机网络/HTTP协议"},"next":{"title":"路由协议","link":"post/计算机网络/路由协议"},"plink":"https://beginc.github.io/post/计算机网络/DNS协议/","toc":[{"id":"dns层次","title":"DNS层次","index":"1","children":[{"id":"根域","title":"根域","index":"1.1"},{"id":"顶级域","title":"顶级域","index":"1.2"},{"id":"二级域","title":"二级域","index":"1.3"}]},{"id":"dns解析过程","title":"DNS解析过程","index":"2","children":[{"id":"递归解析","title":"递归解析","index":"2.1"},{"id":"反复解析","title":"反复解析","index":"2.2"}]}]}